00:04:53.510 --> 00:04:54.720
it will attract more people

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:56.040
to the Xiuzhen District.

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:58.070
And you can take this opportunity
to promote

00:04:58.070 --> 00:05:00.000
