00:08:17.510 --> 00:08:19.110
I fear that if he's punished,

00:08:19.310 --> 00:08:20.310
after he returns,

00:08:20.600 --> 00:08:22.860
he'll treat me even worse.

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:23.770
Besides,

00:08:24.390 --> 00:08:26.190
